[
  "Satyanarayana Chava is the founder and CEO of Laurus Labs, a pharma and biotech company in Hyderabad, in southern India.",
  "Chava worked in the pharma sector for two decades before starting Laurus Labs as an R&D firm in 2005. ",
  "Today, the $658 million (revenue) company supplies pharma ingredients for drugs to treat HIV, cancer, asthma and diabetes. ",
  "Chava remains passionate about research spending 25% of his time in the labs and getting involved with new products."
